snippet.title: ROBOTICS;NOTES DOUBLE PACK Trailer | NSW, PS4
snippet.description:
ROBOTICS;NOTES DOUBLE PACK releases on October 13, 2020 (NA) and October 16, 2020 (EU) for Nintendo Switch™ and PlayStation®4 with a Day One Edition!
ROBOTICS;NOTES DOUBLE PACK Day One Edition includes ROBOTICS;NOTES ELITE and ROBOTICS;NOTES DaSH, as well as 4 pin badges featuring main characters from both games. The pin badges are exclusive to the Day One Edition and won't be reprinted, so place your pre-order now to secure this limited item!

Find out more about the ROBOTICS;NOTES DOUBLE PACK here: 
http://spike-chunsoft.com/ROBOTICSNOTES/

ROBOTICS;NOTES ELITE Steam® Store Page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1111380/ROBOTICSNOTES_ELITE/

ROBOTICS;NOTES DaSH Steam® Store Page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1111390/ROBOTICSNOTES_DaSH/

#ROBOTICSNOTES
